title: Check Out The Vibrant Poster Of Phillauri | Ft. Anushka, Diljit & Suraj Sharma

organizations.name: fox star studios and clean slate films

text: tweet Phillauri’s 1st look poster has been released by its makers, after putting up the trailer on Youtube today morning. This vibrant poster features Anushka Sharma, who’s playing a friendly ghost. Suraj Sharma and Diljit Dosanjh too feature on the poster. Check out the poster right here: Anushka Sharma and Diljit Dosanjh Starrer Phillauri Poster Directed by Anshai Lal and produced by Fox Star Studios and Clean Slate Films, Phillauri is set to hit the screens on 24th March.
